title: SPY's Happy Hour—February 7th, 2014—with mmx and Dr. Edith Eger - Part One
description: Watch SPY President and CEO, Michael Marckx, welcome Auschwitz survivor, author and motivational speaker Dr. Edith Eger to SPY's Headquarters as he speaks about adapting our views, sharing positivity and shaping the happy in our own lives.
